tb: O God, you sent your blessed Son, the seed of the woman, that
    he might crush the serpent’s head and make all creation new:
    Grant that, having this hope, we may purify ourselves as he is
    pure; that, when he comes again with power and great glory,
    we may be made like him in his eternal and glorious kingdom;
    through Jesus Christ our Lord. **Amen.**

