st: the collect
v:celebrant: The Lord be with you.
v:people: And with your spirit.
v:celebrant: Let us pray.
tb: O God, you made this most holy night to shine with the glory
    of the Lord’s resurrection: Stir up in your Church that Spirit
    of adoption which is given to us in Baptism, that we, being
    renewed both in body and mind, may worship you in sincerity
    and truth; through Jesus Christ our Lord, who lives and reigns
    with you, in the unity of the Holy Spirit, one God, now and for
    ever. **Amen.**

